      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "We used an unmasked \"e2v CCD 55-30\" sensor mounted on a ZIMPOL camera [CITATION_1] and operated the ZIMPOL system only in its intensity mode (Stokes I)."
